Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:43.04,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走出黑暗 重获新生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:46.12,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直至光芒 照亮结局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:49.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}丑恶嘴脸 咒骂不止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:52.25,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我的最后一战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:59.97,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恶魔脸孔之下 一副天使面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:06.73,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩童绞尽脑汁 只为保护手中硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:13.23,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恶魔脸孔之下 一副天使面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:20.24,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩童手中 紧攥最后一枚硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:23.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毁灭与重生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:26.45,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你才是真正的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:19.05,op-en,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:43.04,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let's start a new life from the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:46.12,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Until the light reveals the end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:49.92,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sinister faces, growing curses
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:52.25,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is my last war
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:59.97,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels playing disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:06.73,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling to their coins squeezing out their wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:13.23,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels planning disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:20.24,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling on to their very last coins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:23.20,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Destruction and regeneration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:26.45,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You are the real enemy
